---
title: Baconlicious Burgers with Crispy Potatoes and a Creamy Herb Wedge Salad
description: Calling all bacon lovers! These bodacious, bacon-fied burgers were created just for you. All-beef patties are crusted in steak seasoning, seared to juicy perfection, then topped with melty gouda, bacon-fat-caramelized onions, slices of bacon, and a creamy mustard sauce. They’re tucked into buttery brioche buns and served alongside crispy potatoes and crunchy romaine wedges topped with—you guessed it—more bacon, diced tomatoes, and a creamy ranch dressing. This dish is positively bursting with smoky, savory flavors guaranteed to knock any bacon aficionado's socks off.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5d893e405b2c714aa44d35a3-541935da.jpg
